frames.caption: A beautifully arranged meal featuring a steaming dish of spiced meat cubes garnished with red chili and served on a banana leaf. Accompanying the main dish is a bowl of fluffy white rice and several small bowls containing various side dishes and condiments. The presentation is vibrant and inviting, with steam rising from the hot food, suggesting a freshly prepared meal.
